column18: The purpose of this survey is to get a better understanding of dining hall preferences. Your participation is anonymous and voluntary, and no identifying information will be collected. Responses for this survey will not be shared outside of an academic environment. You participating is appreciated. If you consent to taking this survey please click "I consent" in the field below. Once you click to continue, please respond to each prompt to the best of your abilities.
column20: What is your class year? ex. 2024 or 2024J
column22: What Smith neighborhood do you live in?
column23: Based on this situation, how likely are you to agree with the following statements? - I would sit down and eat at this dining hall
column24: Based on this situation, how likely are you to agree with the following statements? - I would go find a new dining hall to have dinner at
column25: Based on this situation, how likely are you to agree with the following statements? - I would take the food to go
column26: Based on this situation, how likely are you to agree with the following statements? - I would enjoy eating at this dining hall
